hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm on a course at the moment advantages of studying drugs by generic names He derides the lack of risk-taking he sees around him: “That’s the problem with everything at the moment, politics, music, art. No one wants to do something different – ‘If we do what happened last time it will work.’ Everything needs to be beige.” He doesn’t tend to watch other comedians much either. “Nothing makes me laugh anymore which is a shame,” he says. “You sometimes see a comedian and you think, ‘I saw all that when I was an eight-year-old kid’. The next big thing is usually not the next big thing.”
